The second installment of¬†Anteprima, an Italian experiential fashion pop-up that launches Italian fashion brands on the American market, will return to New York City this November with a vintage-themed edition and eight dynamic Italian fashion brands. Anteprima, which translates to ‚Äúpreview‚Äù in English, will be taking over SoHo, NY from October 31 to November 10, with two special events on November 5th and 7th.
Surrounded by shareable experiences, Instagrammable corners, and art walls, visitors will have the chance to engage with every vertical of the Italian culture from fashion to food and design.
